Privacy Policy

Effective Date: [February 9 2025]
App Name: [PlateLoader]

Overview

This app is designed to be fully offline and privacy-first. We do not collect, transmit, store, or share any personal data.

Data Collection
	•	The app does not collect personal information.
	•	The app does not use analytics, tracking, advertising, or third-party SDKs.
	•	The app does not require an account or login.

Local Data Storage
	•	All workout data (including workouts, sets, reps, and weights) is stored locally on your device only.
	•	This data never leaves your device.
	•	We do not have access to your data under any circumstances.

Network Usage
	•	The app does not connect to the internet.
	•	No data is transmitted to servers, cloud services, or third parties.

Third Parties
	•	This app does not integrate with third-party services.
	•	No data is shared with advertisers, analytics providers, or external platforms.

Data Deletion
	•	You can delete all stored data at any time by deleting the app from your device.
	•	Any in-app reset or factory reset option permanently removes all local data.

Children’s Privacy
	•	This app does not knowingly collect data from anyone, including children under 13.

Changes to This Policy

If this privacy policy changes in the future, the updated version will be included within the app or its distribution listing.

Contact

If you have questions about this privacy policy, you can contact the developer at:
